channel.title: Tutorial requests!
channel.description:
hey i have searched alot of places and i havent had much luck really i need the following TUT's for my server please people help someone out here!!! this would help many people!!!
There is a lot of stuff needed if you know how to code most of these pm and i can send you my msn and we can talk, the only way i can repay you is by giving you 60% credits for making my server, making you and admin on my server, my thanks and sending you music over msn lawl
[b]Ok So Heres What I Need!!![/b]
[ul][li]Full working tzhaar pits with minigames and shops[/li] [li]Full working mage bow[/li] [li]Full working specials[/li] [li]Full working style of skill capes[/li] [li]Full working Hair dresser[/li] [li]Full working dwarf multicannon[/li] [li]Full working obby rings[/li] [li]Full working throwing axes with rune special[/li] [li]Fixed range exp for bows throwing axes and cannon[/li] [li]Fixed attacking and dieing for most monsters[/li] [li]Fixed doors for most places including fally,draynor,draynor manor,ape atoll,al kahrid etc..main citys[/li] [li]Fixed wilderness,with proper pking[/li] [li]Full working magic and ancients[/li] [li]needing wc/pic to mine and wc[/li] [li]Full firemaking[/li] [li]Full fletching[/li] [li]Full leather,dragonhide and gem crafting[/li] [li]Full fishing (with fishing spots in catherby)[/li] [li]Full cooking[/li] [li]Fixed times for weapons/entangle etc..[/li] [li]Autocasting for staffs[/li] [li]fixed barrows specials[/li] [li]200/200 working stats[/li] [li]fix the hp so you can still lose health after hp maxes out[/li] [li]Fixed herblore[/li] [li]Added seeds(allotment and trees just)[/li] [li][s]Fixed D'hide levels[/s][/li][/ul]
once i have obtained something of this list i shall post a link and cross the ones i have got out so i can help others, dont worry full credits to those who made the TUT's and who helped me find these
